README
======

Make by
Kevin "qwazerty" Houdebert
houdeb_k
EPITA 2015 - ACDC

This script purpose is to easily generate all the needed files to start a
project such as Makefile, Doxyfile, etc...

To use this script, create an empty project folder, and call the script with
the project name as argument. For example:

42sh$ mkdir test-project
42sh$ cd test-project
42sh$ ~/project_gen/gen.sh test_project
42sh$ ls
AUTHORS  Makefile.am  README  bootstrap  configure.ac  doc  src

With 42sh$ representing your prompt.
